tweet: Is your Thanksgiving menu also your day after Thanksgiving menu? Be sure to refrigerate your leftovers at 40°F or colder within 2 hours of preparation to prevent food poisoning and foodborne illnesses. #HappyTurkeyDay #HappyThanksgiving #Dayton  https://t.co/uRgjKJnACM
